
1.encoding and decoding example:

<html>
<head>
<title>javascript</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=pink>
<script>
document.write(escape("Hello world"));
document.write("<br>");
document.write(escape("! #D$&()<>"));
document.write("<br>");
document.write(unescape("Hello%20world"));
document.write("<br>");
document.write(unescape("%21%20%23D%24%26%28%29%3C%3E"));
document.write("<br>");
</script>
</body>
</html>
